{"priority": "blocker", "kind": "bug", "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}ts=1694483"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo", "uuid": "{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}"}, "links": {"attachments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1354/attachments_page=1.json"}, "self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1354.json"}, "watch": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1354/watch"}, "comments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1354/comments_page=1.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/1354/abi-problem-for-gazebo4"}, "vote": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/1354/vote"}}, "reporter": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "title": "ABI problem for gazebo4", "component": {"name": "abi", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/components/141596.json"}}}, "votes": 0, "watches": 4, "content": {"raw": "In pull request #1284 (merged to gazebo_2.2), two new private member variables were [added to ODELink](#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-request/1284/issue-243-fix-link-getworldlinearaccel-and/diff#chg-gazebo/physics/ode/ODELink.hh). This [doesn't affect ABI for gazebo_2.2](http://build.osrfoundation.org/view/API_ABI%20checker/job/gazebo-any_to_any-abichecker-precise-amd64/129/API_ABI_report/) because the ode headers weren't installed in 2.2.\r\n\r\nThe ode headers are now installed as of pull request #1183, which has just been released in gazebo 4.1.0, which was just before pull request #1284 was merged.\r\n\r\nSo, when we merge gazebo_2.2 forward, it will [break ABI for gazebo4](http://build.osrfoundation.org/job/gazebo-any_to_any-abichecker-precise-amd64/130/API_ABI_report/).", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>In <a href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1284/issue-243-fix-link-getworldlinearaccel-and\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">pull request #1284</a> (merged to gazebo_2.2), two new private member variables were <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-request/1284/issue-243-fix-link-getworldlinearaccel-and/diff#chg-gazebo/physics/ode/ODELink.hh\" rel=\"nofollow\">added to ODELink</a>. This <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"http://build.osrfoundation.org/view/API_ABI%20checker/job/gazebo-any_to_any-abichecker-precise-amd64/129/API_ABI_report/\" rel=\"nofollow\">doesn't affect ABI for gazebo_2.2</a> because the ode headers weren't installed in 2.2.</p>\n<p>The ode headers are now installed as of <a href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1183/install-physics-headers\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">pull request #1183</a>, which has just been released in gazebo 4.1.0, which was just before <a href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1284/issue-243-fix-link-getworldlinearaccel-and\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">pull request #1284</a> was merged.</p>\n<p>So, when we merge gazebo_2.2 forward, it will <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"http://build.osrfoundation.org/job/gazebo-any_to_any-abichecker-precise-amd64/130/API_ABI_report/\" rel=\"nofollow\">break ABI for gazebo4</a>.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "closed", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2014-12-02T19:29:57.576173+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-09-14T19:44:37.006819+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 1354}